# Group Mensagem

## assignment [/assignment]

### Create a new assignment [POST]

+ Relation: post

+ Request Criar um assignment

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json
            Content-Type: application/json
    + Attributes
    
        + name (string) - the assignment 
        + description (string) - A description of assignment
        + date(number) - time the 'assignment'
        + conclude(boolean) - conclui the 'assignment'
        + cancel(boolean)  - cancel of 'assignment'      

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Created)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
+ Attributes (Error)

