### Alter assignment [PUT]
+ Relation: update
+ Request Change one assignment
    + Headers

            Accept: application/json
            Content-Type: application/json
    + Attributes 
        
        + name (string)
        + description (string)
        + date(number) 
        + conclude(boolean)
        + cancel(boolean)  

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Created)

+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)


### Excluir assignment [DELETE]
+ Relation: DELETE
+ Response 204 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Id)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Error)

# Data Structures

## assignment (object)
+ subject (string) - Assunto da assignment
+ body (string) - Corpo da assignment

## assignmentUpdate (assignment)
+ id_assignment (number) - Id da assignment

## Created (object)
+ id (number) - Id gerado

## Id (object)
+ id (number) - Id a ser processado

## Error (object)
+ code: 400 (number) - Status code
+ message (string) - Mensagem do status
+ description (string) - Descrição do status


## Multi (object)
+ id (number) - Código da entidade
+ code: 200 (number) - Status code
+ message (string) - Descrição do status


## User (object)
+ id (number) - Código do usuário
+ name (string) - Nome do usuário
+ token (string) - Token do usuário conectado